[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    228[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;235;203;139m**[38;2;235;203;139mOverlap: Security Finding 1 (push PHI) and Architecture Finding 7 (portal_push architecture undefined).[38;2;235;203;139m**[38;2;192;197;206m Both experts flagged the portal_push channel for the same underlying reason: it appears in the candidate list but has no real architectural or security treatment. These are two views of one gap. Resolution: treat them as a single issue with two facets (the architecture needs a push component, and that component has specific BAA constraints). Either remove push from the recipe and mention as future work, or add a real push architecture with the BAA-compliant pattern.[K
